<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>律诗 on 思明韵律</title><link>https://simingyunlv.com/form/%E5%BE%8B%E8%AF%97/</link><description>Recent content in 律诗 on 思明韵律</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 06 Oct 2025 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://simingyunlv.com/form/%E5%BE%8B%E8%AF%97/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>敝帚</title><link>https://simingyunlv.com/poems/2025/%E6%95%9D%E5%B8%9A/</link><pubDate>Mon, 06 Oct 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://simingyunlv.com/poems/2025/%E6%95%9D%E5%B8%9A/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;[poem]
和纏相召真，湖畔兩癡人。
研墨滄桑舊，吟毫日月新。
氣同同契合，聲比比貞純。
結集呈錚友，慚惶敝帚珍。
[/poem]&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>